Dallas%3B%20Atlanta%3B%20Los%20Angeles%3B%20San%20Ramon%2C%20CA%3B%20Seattle%3B%20St.%20Louis%3B%20Washington%3B%20Middletown%2C%20NJ%3B%20and%20Bedminster%2C%20NJ.%20The%20company%20previously%20supported%20more%20than%20300%20offices%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20affected%20employees%20faced%20the%20choice%20of%20relocating%20or%20finding%20a%20new%20job%2C%20with%20some%2018%2C000%20management%20employees%20opting%20to%20return%20to%20one%20of%20the%20hubs%2C%20according%20to%20AT%26amp%3BT's%20proxy%20statement%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20some%20workers%20who%20may%20have%20gotten%20used%20to%20hybrid%20schedules%20will%20soon%20be%20required%20to%20log%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20five%20days%20a%20week%20at%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20majority%20of%20our%20employees%20and%20leaders%20never%20stopped%20working%20on%20location%20for%20the%20full%20work%20week%20%E2%80%94%20including%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20multiple%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20Reddit%20users%20on%20the%20AT%26amp%3BT%20subreddit%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20whether%20the%20offices%20have%20enough%20capacity%20for%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20told%20BI%20it%20is%20updating%20its%20facilities%20amid%20the%20policy%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20continue%20to%20evolve%20our%20model%2C%20we%20are%20enhancing%20our%20facilities%20and%20workspaces%2C%20adapting%20our%20benefits%20programs%2C%20and%20incorporating%20best%20practices%20to%20ensure%20our%20employees%20are%20best%20equipped%20to%20serve%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20BI%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-delays-full-rto-some-staff-workspace-shortages-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAmazon%20was%20delaying%20its%205-days-in-of