h-for-Jobs%20Scam%26quot%3B%20in%20Goa%2C%20claiming%20she%20was%20involved%20in%20corrupt%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20statements%20were%20broadcast%20live%20on%20multiple%20national%20and%20regional%20news%20channels%20and%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%2C%20where%20they%20have%20garnered%20significant%20views%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defamation%20suit%20asserts%20that%20these%20false%20accusations%20were%20made%20without%20any%20credible%20evidence%2C%20causing%20harm%20to%20Sulakshana%20Sawant's%20integrity%20and%20public%20image.%20The%20statements%20made%20by%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20were%20not%20only%20damaging%20but%20were%20also%20broadcasted%20and%20shared%20extensively%2C%20amplifying%20the%20false%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defamation%20occurred%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20where%20Sanjay%20Singh%20made%20direct%20accusations%20against%20Sulakshana%20Sawant's%20integrity%20and%20her%20involvement%20in%20the%20scam%2C%20thereby%20damaging%20her%20reputation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20press%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20official%20press%20note%2C%20the%20legal%20action%20sought%20by%20Sulakshana%20Sawant%20includes%20seeking%20Rs%20100%20crores%20as%20damages%20for%20defamation%2C%20a%20permanent%20injunction%20against%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20his%20associates%2C%20restraining%20them%20from%20making%20or%20publishing%20defamatory%20statements%2C%20videos%2C%20or%20articles%20about%20her%20on%20any%20platform%2C%20including%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sawant%20has%20also%20demanded%20a%20public%20apology%20from%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20clarifying%20the%20falsehood%20of%20his%20statements%20and%20the%20defamatory%20video%2C%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20sought%20an%20injunction%20to%20prevent%20further%20defamatory%20statements%20by%20Mr%20Singh%20or%20his%20associates%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Ms%20Sawant%20has%20requested%20the%20court%20to%20grant%20the%20costs%20of%20the%20suit%20and%20any%20other%20appropriate%20reliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20press%20note%2C%20the%20baseless%20and%20defamatory%20statements%20made%20by%20Sanjay%20Singh%20are%20%26quot%3B....Over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20corruption%20and%20bribery%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20job%20creation.%20Even%20the%20wife%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Pramod%20Sawant%20has%20been%20named%20in%20the%20scandal%2C%20along%20with%20several%20of%20his%20ministers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20small%20issue%20--%20it%20is%20a%20massive%20job%20scam%20involving%20corruption%20and%20bribery%20in%20Goa%2C%20with%20direct%20involvement%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20ministers.%20The%20names%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20wife%20and%20various%20brokers%20have%20been%20revealed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20job%20bribery%20scam%20became%20even%20more%20serious%20when%20the%20then-Governor%2C%20Satyapal%20Malik%2C%20publicly%20stated%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Pramod%20Sawant's%20wife%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20job%20scam%2C%20accepting%20bribes%20for%20jobs%2C%20committing%20corruption%2C%20and%20demanding%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20clearly%20indicates%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Goa%20and%20his%20entire%20family%20are%20involved%20in%20accepting%20bribes%20under%20the%20pretence%20of%20offering%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20aspirants%20had%20lodged%20complaints%20in%20Goa%20alleging%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20pay%20lakhs%20to%20some%20people%20who%20promised%20to%20facilitate%20jobs%20in%20the%20Goa%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECM%20Pramod%20Sawant%20had%20said%20that%20the%20state%2