0breathe%20and%20she%20was%20left%20to%20soil%20herself%20in%20nappies%20as%20she%20was%20prevented%20from%20using%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESara%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20her%20bed%20in%20August%202023%20at%20her%20empty%20family%20home.%20A%20post-mortem%20examination%20revealed%20she%20had%2071%20fresh%20injuries%20and%20at%20least%2025%20broken%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECavanagh%20described%20Sara%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20little%20girl%20full%20of%20personality%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bfeisty%26quot%3B%20and%20loved%20to%20sing%20and%20dance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20she%20died%2C%20Sharif%20hit%20Sara%20twice%20in%20the%20stomach%20with%20the%20metal%20leg%20of%20a%20high-chair%20as%20she%20lay%20unconscious%20on%20her%20stepmother's%20lap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sadists'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20and%20Batool%20were%20found%20guilty%20last%20week%20after%20a%2010-week%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20uncle%20Faisal%20Malik%2C%2029%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20causing%20or%20allowing%20her%20death.%20He%20was%20jailed%20for%2016%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESara's%20birth%20mother%2C%20Olga%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20court%20that%20her%20daughter%20is%20%26quot%3Bnow%20an%20angel%20who%20looks%20down%20on%20us%20from%20heaven%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20this%20day%20I%20can't%20understand%20how%20someone%20can%20be%20such%20a%20sadist%20to%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20called%20the%20case%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20and%20distressing%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20had%20ever%20had%20to%20deal%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20Sara%20died%2C%20the%20three%20adults%20fled%20their%20home%20in%20Woking%2C%20southwest%20of%20London%2C%20and%20flew%20to%20Pakistan%20with%20five%20other%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%2C%20a%20taxi-driver%2C%20phoned%20the%20police%20from