people%20say%20they're%20'allergic%20to%20their%20period.'%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20the%20autoimmune%20skin%20condition%20that%20causes%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20scratching%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d7606c531c315b88d26b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProgesterone%20dermatitis%20can%20cause%20skin%20reactions.%3Cp%3EMariia%20Vitkovska%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EProgesterone%20dermatitis%20is%20a%20rare%20immune%20sensitivity%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESymptoms%20present%20like%20common%20skin%20conditions%2C%20including%20eczema%20and%20hives%2C%20or%20allergic%20reactions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20weigh%20in%20to%20help%20you%20understand%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAutoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20is%20a%20rare%20condition%20that%20can%20occur%20when%20progesterone%20rises%20during%20a%20woman's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-life-balance-overworked-lawyer-period-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can%20cause%20a%20physical%20reaction%20that%20may%20present%20differently%20depending%20on%20the%20person%2C%20but%20symptoms%20often%20mirror%20skin%20conditions%20like%20eczema%2C%20hives%2C%20or%20other%20allergic%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Purvi%20Parikh%2C%20an%20allergist%20and%20immunologist%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20caused%20by%20the%20immune%20system%20becoming%20sensitive%20to%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20hormone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20your%20own%20immune%20system%20starts%20forming%20either%20an%20allergy%20or%20a%20sensitivity%20to%20progesterone.%20We%20have%20progesterone%20in%20our%20body%20as%20a%20hormone%2C%20and%20so%20normally%2C%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20allergic%20to%20it%20because%20it's%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Parikh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESymptoms%20of%20the%20condition%20usually%20appear%20between%203%20and%2010%20days%20before%20the%20first%20day%20of%20your%20period%2C%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fmenstrual-cycle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluteal%20phase%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20menstruation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20know%20is%20there%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fseasonal-allergies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esensitivity%20or%20an%20allergy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20reaction%20to%20the%20high%20progesterone%20levels%20that%20occur%20during%20the%20luteal%20phase%2C%20which%20is%20directly%20before%20the%20menstrual%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Angela%20Brimhall%2C%20a%20board-certified%20holistic%20dermatologist%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e52d9d9e-1121-4f26-8019-d63fc59ab14b%5C%22%3EAre%20some%20more%20likely%20than%20others%20to%20develop%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20taking%20hormonal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fbirth-control%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirth%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prevent%20unwanted%20pregnancy%2C%20reduce%20the%20symptoms%20of%20premenstrual%20syndrome%2C%20or%20another%20reason%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20benefits%20associated%20with%20it.%20But%20depending%20on%20the%20type%20of%20birth%20control%20you%20take%2C%20it%20could%20also%20increase%20your%20chance%20of%20developing%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20women%2C%20taking%20outside%20progesterone%2C%20or%20what%20we%20call%20'exogenous%20progesterone%2C'%20either%20in%20the%20form%20of%20birth%20control%20or%20for%20other%20reasons%2C%20can%20sometimes%20cause%20your%20immune%20system%20to%20become%20sensitive%20or%20hypersensitive%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Parikh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParikh%20said%20that%20during%20the%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20natural%20progesterone%20rises%2C%20and%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-gut-health-gut-gardening-brain-immune-system-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimmune%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20begin%20to%20experience%20the%20hormone%20as%20something%20you're%20allergic%20to%2C%20with%20increased%20risk%20for%20those%20taking%20forms%20of%20progesterone%20from%20outside%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Somi%20Javaid%2C%20a%20board-certified%20OB-GYN%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20there's%20no%20known%20genetic%20predisposition%20to%20developing%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fautoimmune.org%2Fdisease-information%2Fprogesterone-dermatitis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAutoimmune%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20while%20any%20premenopausal%20woman%20could%20develop%20the%20condition%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20rare%20in%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac928a88-58dd-45c0-b347-e241031cc8f8%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20develop%20the%20condition%2C%20what%20can%20you%20expect%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20develop%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%2C%20you%20may%20experience%20physical%20symptoms%20similar%20to%20an%20allergic%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20present%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20skin%20manifestations%2C%26quot%3B%20Javaid%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20something%20that%20looks%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Feczema-treatment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeczema%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hives%2C%20angioedema%2C%20erythema%20multiforme%2C%20vesicles%20that%20look%20like%20papules%2C%20mouth%20erosions%2C%20or%20itching.%20It's%20a%20hypersensitivity%2C%20so%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20an%20allergic%20reaction.%20That's%20why%20people%20say%20they%20feel%20like%20they're%20allergic%20to%20their%20cycle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20type%20of%20treatment%20that%20will%20be%20most%20beneficial%20to%20you%20depends%20on%20the%20specific%20symptoms%20you%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst-line%20therapies%20can%20be%20topical%20steroids%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fcorticosteroids%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoral%20steroids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20antihistamines%2C%20or%20a%20medication%20to%20help%20block%20the%20product%20production%20of%20progesterone%2C%26quot%3B%20Javaid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20medication%2C%20Javaid%20some%20basic%20lifestyle%20changes%20could%20benefit%20people%20with%20progesterone%20dermatitis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20that%20helps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fhormone-replacement-therapy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulate%20hormones%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20also%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Javaid%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaking%20sure%20you're%20sleeping%2C%20managing%20your%20stress.%20If%20we're%20talking%20about%20an%20inflammatory%20response%2C%20limiting%20things%20you%20put%20in%20your%20body%20that%20promote%20inflammation%2C%20like%20fried%20foods%2C%20processed%20foods%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20alcohol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc1686a4-538c-4502-9680-a21c88e1fbe2%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20you%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20and%20regular%20allergy%20symptoms%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20symptoms%20of%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20spot%20as%20they%20can%20appear%20similar%20to%20allergies%20or%20common%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskin-symptoms-of-health-conditions-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskin%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20before%20you%20write%20your%20symptoms%20off%20as%20allergies%2C%20take%20note%20of%20when%20they%20worsen%20and%20how%20often%20you%20experience%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavaid%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20there's%20no%20single%20diagnostic%20tool%20for%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%2C%20paying%20attention%20to%20your%20menstrual%20cycle%20can%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fperiod-tracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETracking%20your%20cycles%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20your%20symptoms%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20key%20diagnostic%20tool%20and%20what%20you%20should%20do%20to%20help%20yourself%20when%20you%20go%20to%20your%20provider%20to%20make%20that%20diagnosis%2C%26quot%3B%20Javaid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParikh%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20noticing%20a%20clear%20cyclical%20pattern%20to%20your%20symptoms%20that%20worsens%20during%20your%20menstrual%20cycle%20is%20a%20warning%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0de9cc8-b9ab-4005-9265-d1bc60a5598e%5C%22%3EWhy%20you%20may%20not%20have%20heard%20of%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20before%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20not%20have%20heard%20of%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20because%20there's%20little%20existing%20research%20on%20it.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8642151%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bless%20than%20200%20cases%20of%20this%20rare%20condition%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20literature.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20lack%20of%20research%20could%20indicate%20the%20condition%20is%20rare%2C%20it%20could%20also%20indicate%20a%20larger%20issue%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-technology-women-healthcare-access-gaps-femtech-platform-medical-providers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen's%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20underdiagnosed%2C%26quot%3B%20Parikh%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20women%20in%20general%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20traditionally%2C%20their%20concerns%20and%20symptoms%20may%20not%20be%20taken%20as%20seriously%20or%20may%20be%20disregarded%20by%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20on%20that.%20So%20initially%2C%20people%20may%20have%20presented%20with%20symptoms%2C%20but%20they%20weren't%20diagnosed%20as%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20you%20have%20autoimmune%20progesterone%20dermatitis%2C%20a%20great%20first%20step%20is%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fwho-to-talk-to-about-mental-health-struggles-family-physician-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsult%20a%20medical%20provider%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20discuss%20your%20symptoms%20and%20potential%20treatment%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-progesterone-dermatitis-symptoms-treatment-options-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734478742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d7741d90e3bcf31d6ce2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-progesterone-dermatitis-symptoms-treatment-options-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20allergist%2C%20dermatologist%2C%20and%20OB-GYN%20explain%20how%20progesterone%20dermatitis%20presents%20and%20which%20treatments%20can%20help%20you%20ease%20symptoms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cgriffin%40businessinsider.com%20(Cailey%20Griffin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22h