ccess%20for%20cleaning%2C%20and%20the%20slatted%20exit%20captures%20litter%20before%20it%20can%20end%20up%20on%20your%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272f219ba-169f-4392-8155-8857c6a4d0cf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20with%20storage%5C%22%3EBest%20with%20storage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20gain%20extra%20space%20with%20your%20litter%20box%20enclosure%2C%20the%20Tucker%20and%20Murphy%20Laskie%20may%20be%20a%20good%20option.%20The%20steps%20that%20take%20your%20cat%20to%20an%20elevated%20lounging%20area%20double%20as%20roomy%20drawers%20to%20stash%20cleaning%20tools%20or%20anything%20else%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20handy.%20It%20has%20two%20entrances%2C%20both%207.75-inch%20squares.%20This%20is%20good%20for%20your%20cat%20because%20two%20exit%20points%20can%20help%20keep%20your%20cat%20from%20feeling%20trapped%20in%20the%20confined%20space%20and%20offer%20a%20quick%20escape%20if%20they're%20being%20ambushed%20by%20another%20furry%20family%20member%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmed.vt.edu%2Fpeople%2Ffaculty%2Ffreeman-mark.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Mark%20Freeman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20community%20practice%20at%20the%20Virginia%20Tech%20Virginia-Maryland%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20enclosure%20is%20made%20of%20MDF%20wood%20and%20weighs%20just%20under%2060%20pounds%20when%20assembled.%20Assembly%20may%20take%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20between%20two%20people%2C%20according%20to%20reviewers.%20Also%20note%20the%20drawers%20don't%20come%20with%20knobs%2C%20which%20one%20reviewer%20says%20can%20make%20them%20a%20little%20tricky%20to%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eec147d7-0f60-4d69-9134-bd7467e38611%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20a%20corner%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20a%20corner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20essential%20to%20provide%20your%20cat%20with%20a%20litter%20box%20in%20a%20low-traffic%20spot%20to%20help%20keep%20their%20stress%20to%20a%20minimum.%20When%20using%20even%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-litter-box%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20cat%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20stressful%2C%20that's%20when%20cats%20resort%20to%20eliminating%20elsewhere.%20Lugones%20says%20peeing%20or%20pooping%20outside%20the%20litter%20box%20is%20the%20number%20one%20reason%20cats%20are%20surrendered%20to%20the%20shelter%20and%20a%20common%20reason%20for%20veterinary%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20share%20a%20small%20home%20or%20apartment%20with%20cats%2C%20you%20might%20find%20yourself%20with%20limited%20options%20for%20where%20to%20put%20the%20box.%20But%20that's%20where%20the%20Kitangle%20Corner%20Kitty%20litter%20box%20comes%20in%20handy.%20Its%20triangular%20design%20makes%20it%20suitable%20for%20even%20the%20most%20awkward%20spaces%2C%20like%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20many%20options%20for%20litter%20boxes%20that%20fit%20into%20an%20out-of-the-way%20corner%2C%20but%20Kitangle%20offers%20the%20best%20we've%20seen.%20It's%20made%20of%20sturdy%20polypropylene%20plastic%20and%20has%20a%20seamless%20design%20that's%20more%20spacious%20than%20many%20traditional%20covered%20boxes.%20The%20removable%20lid%20helps%20simplify%20cleaning%2C%20and%20a%20one-piece%20base%20helps%20keep%20urine%20from%20seeping%20into%20cracks.%20The%20entry%2C%20which%20is%208.75%20inches%20high%20and%208.5%20inches%20wide%2C%20is%20just%206%20inches%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20so%20most%20cats%20should%20be%20able%20to%20enter%20and%20exit%20without%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ebb7238-508f-4511-a974-cd4e038d6677%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20bathrooms%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20bathrooms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20share%20a%20bathroom%20with%20your%20cat%2C%20this%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20litter%20box%20furniture%20has%20extra%20counter%20space%20that%20can%20be%20a%20great%20solution.%20And%20speaking%20of%20extra%20space%2C%20the%20interior%20of%20this%20litter%20box%20enclosure%20has%20plenty%20of%20room.%20Lugones%20says%20it's%20important%20to%20choose%20a%20litter%20box%20that%20allows%20your%20cat%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20turn%20around%20without%20touching%20any%20sides%2C%20including%20their%20tail.%20The%20design%20of%20this%20generously%20sized%20litter%20box%20allows%20your%20cat%20to%20do%20just%20that.%20Plus%2C%20the%20ventilation%20slots%20on%20each%20side%20allow%20for%20necessary%20airflow%20and%20a%20full%20view%20of%20the%20room.%20This%20litter%20box%20enclosure%20has%20one%20entry%2C%20a%207.9-inch%20square%20at%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20enclosure%20is%20made%20of%20Ecoflex%2C%20a%20super%20wood%2Fplastic%20composite%20that's%20resistant%20to%20both%20liquid%20and%20odors.%20In%20short%2C%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20it%20soaking%20up%20cat%20pee%20or%20absorbing%20litter%20box%20odors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269ea0447-3061-4617-a29f-d27682b5ee28%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20large%20cats%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20large%20cats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20big%20cat%20that%20needs%20a%20large%20litter%20box%2C%20furniture%20may%20not%20be%20a%20workable%20option.%20A%20privacy%20screen%2C%20however%2C%20can%20keep%20the%20box%20out%20of%20view%20without%20sacrificing%20your%20cat's%20comfort.%20This%20screen%20features%20semi-transparent%20plastic%20panels%2C%20a%20bamboo%20wood%20frame%2C%20and%20two-way%20hinges%20so%20you%20can%20position%20it%20into%20a%20%26quot%3BZ%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BU%26quot%3B%20shape.%20This%20can%20create%20a%20clear%20entry%20and%20exit%20from%20the%20box%20to%20help%20minimize%20litter%20tracking%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20add%20a%20litter%20mat.%20The%20screen%20itself%20is%20fairly%20light%20%E2%80%94%20just%20under%208%20pounds%20%E2%80%94%20so%20it's%20possible%20a%20cat%20could%20knock%20it%20down%20in%20a%20fit%20of%20post-bathroom%20zoomies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeVoss%20says%20cats%20tend%20to%20prefer%20litter%20box%20furniture%20that%20provides%20ample%20space%20to%20do%20their%20business%20and%20isn't%20enclosed%20on%20all%20four%20sides.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20recommend%20little%20box%20furniture%20that%20is%20open%20in%20the%20back%2C%20very%20tall%2C%20and%20has%20an%20exit%20path%20on%20each%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Customizing%20furniture%20to%20check%20all%20those%20boxes%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20costly.%20However%2C%20this%20enclosure%20satisfies%20all%20DeVoss's%20must-haves%20for%20cats%20of%20all%20ages%20and%20sizes%20%E2%80%94%20for%20under%20%2470.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221cddaa5f-fed4-4171-800d-f3da93a72b06%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20senior%20cats%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20senior%20cats%2C%20kittens%2C%20and%20cats%20with%20special%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20cats%20are%20agile%20enough%20to%20use%20any%20type%20of%20litter%20box.%20Senior%20cats%20and%20cats%20with%20arthritis%20may%20find%20it%20painful%20to%20use%20litter%20boxes%20with%20high%20sides%20or%20furniture%20with%20steps.%20Young%20kittens%2C%20who%20have%20short%20legs%20and%20limited%20vertical%20reach%2C%20may%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20accessing%20elevated%20litter%20boxes.%20Cats%20with%20poor%20balance%20and%20vision%2C%20limited%20motor%20skills%2C%20or%20other%20special%20needs%20may%20also%20be%20unable%20to%20use%20elevated%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELow-to-the-ground%20boxes%20without%20steps%20or%20inclines%20can%20better%20accommodate%20these%20cats%2C%20Lugones%20says.%20The%20Qlevo%20litter%20box%20cabinet%2C%20handmade%20and%20sold%20through%20Etsy%2C%20is%20one%20option%20that%20fits%20these%20criteria.%20This%20enclosure%20has%20a%20floor-level%20entryway%20that%20measures%2010%20inches%20by%2016%20inches%2C%20with%20large%20cutouts%20that%20let%20in%20plenty%20of%20light%20and%20air.%20You%20can%20also%20customize%20it%20further%20by%20adding%20a%20second%20entrance%2C%20such%20as%20a%20top%20entry.%20The%20top%20of%20the%20enclosure%20lifts%20up%20for%20easy%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20return%20or%20exchange%20this%20product%2C%20but%20you%20can%20ask%20the%20seller%20any%20questions%20you%20have%20before%20you%20make%20the%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228153c91b-27d5-4b4d-8e3a-50278b88322b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%20speaking%2C%20cats%20prefer%20a%20pristine%20litter%20box%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-litter-box%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20helps%20ensure%20they%20always%20have%20what%20they%20need.%20Yet%20even%20though%20smart%20litter%20boxes%20are%20designed%20to%20help%20reduce%20noise%20and%20odors%2C%20hiding%20the%20litter%20box%20in%20furniture%20still%20has%20its%20perks.%20%26quot%3BWe%20love%20our%20cats%2C%20but%20don't%20necessarily%20need%20to%20observe%20their%20every%20elimination%2C%26quot%3B%20Freeman%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20farmhouse-rustic%20design%20features%20two%20solid%20wood%20sides%20and%20three%20credenza%20doors.%20The%20fourth%20side%20remains%20entirely%20open%20to%20allow%20for%20air%20circulation%20and%20easy%20entry.%20Whisker%20manufactures%20this%20litter%20box%20credenza%2C%20and%20any%20Whisker%20Litter-Robot%20model%20will%20fit%20inside%2C%20along%20with%20its%20ramp.%20The%20large%20design%20should%20also%20accommodate%20most%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%20on%20the%20market.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20once%20assembled%2C%20it%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20move%2C%20as%20it%20weighs%20111%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276ecff9f-8d49-4e44-b515-74a72102104d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20planter%5C%22%3EBest%20planter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20and%20real%20plants%20don't%20always%20coexist%20happily%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20this%20double-duty%20planter%20may%20come%20in%20handy.%20The%20spacious%20hollow%20base%20acts%20as%20your%20cat's%20litter%20box%2C%20and%20the%20faux%20foliage%20on%20top%20adds%20aesthetic%20appeal.%20The%20entry%2C%20a%209-inch%20square%2C%20is%20slightly%20elevated%20to%20prevent%20litter%20from%20being%20kicked%20out.%20You%20can%20also%20add%20a%20high-wall%20lining%20to%20the%20enclosure%20to%20prevent%20leaks%2C%20which%20may%20come%20in%20handy%20if%20you%20have%20an%20enthusiastic%20sprayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20fake%20plant%20may%20not%20do%20much%20to%20freshen%20the%20air%2C%20the%20planter's%20polypropylene%20plastic%20base%20and%20replaceable%20carbon%20filter%20may%20help%20prevent%20odors.%20That's%20because%20plastic%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20trap%20odors%20and%20bodily%20fluids%20than%20porous%20materials%20like%20unfinished%20wood%2C%20Lugones%20says.%20However%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20keep%20any%20litter%20box%20smelling%20fresh%20involves%20scooping%20daily%20and%20deep%20cleaning%20the%20box%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20every%20two%20to%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planter%20consists%20of%20five%20parts%20that%20need%20to%20be%20assembled%3A%20the%20two-part%20base%20that%20twists%20and%20snaps%20securely%2C%20a%20carbon%20filter%2C%20and%20the%20faux%20foliage%20and%20florist%20moss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e5e0e9b-286e-4403-aec8-70486a474ee9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20homes%20with%20dogs%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20homes%20with%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20cats%20don't%20appreciate%20surprise%20guests%20while%20they're%20going%20to%20the%20bathroom.%20That%20includes%20curious%20canines%20who%20might%20like%20to%20stick%20their%20nose%20where%20it%20doesn't%20belong%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20forage%20for%20cat%20poop.%20The%20best%20solution%20is%20to%20place%20the%20litter%20box%20in%20a%20room%20your%20dog%20can't%20access%2C%20DeVoss%20says.%20But%20if%20you%20have%20limited%20space%2C%20Lugones%20says%20litter%20box%20furniture%20can%20be%20an%20excellent%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20top-entry%20litter%20box%20enclosure%20keeps%20your%20cat's%20business%20private%20by%20preventing%20dogs%20from%20getting%20in.%20It%20also%20helps%20keep%20litter%20in%20the%20box%20instead%20of%20scattered%20throughout%20your%20house.%20The%20perforated%20entry%20and%20exit%20platform%20allows%20for%20air%20circulation%20and%20returns%20stray%20litter%20from%20your%20cat's%20paws%20back%20into%20the%20box.%20While%20this%20enclosure%20fits%20most%20standard%20litter%20boxes%2C%20the%20seller%20says%20they're%20happy%20to%20accommodate%20custom%20requests%2C%20like%20a%20larger%20size%20or%20extra%20features%20like%20air%20vents%20or%20another%20door.%20The%20unit%20has%20locking%20wheels%20for%20easy%20movement%20and%20a%20top-opening%20lid%20for%20simple%20cleaning.%20The%20entry%20hole%20at%20the%20top%20is%2010.2%20inches%20in%20diameter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20return%20or%20exchange%20this%20product%2C%20but%20you%20can%20message%20the%20seller%20with%20any%20questions%20before%20purchasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22554de1f2-6e1f-419f-9db1-34aff68cf52b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20cat%20litter%20box%20furniture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recommend%20considering%20these%20essential%20features%20when%20selecting%20the%20best%20litter%20box%20furniture.%20Our%20advice%20is%20based%20on%20information%20from%20our%20experts%2C%20research%2C%20and%20personal%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20your%20litter%20box%20and%20the%20furniture%20that%20houses%20it%20isn't%20large%20enough%20for%20your%20cat%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20turn%20around%20in%2C%20your%20cat%20may%20choose%20to%20eliminate%20elsewhere.%20We%20selected%20litter%20box%20furniture%20suitable%20for%20cats%20of%20all%20sizes%20and%20opted%20for%20pieces%20that%20fit%20well%20in%20small%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessibility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESenior%20cats%2C%20kittens%2C%20and%20special%20needs%20cats%20may%20have%20different%20accessibility%20needs%20than%20other%20cats.%20To%20accommodate%20cats%20with%20mobility%20limitations%2C%20we%20chose%20furniture%20with%20large%20openings%20flush%20or%20just%20slightly%20off%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20viewpoints%20and%20entrances%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20some%20cats%20may%20find%20an%20enclosed%20space%20soothing%2C%20others%20might%20prefer%20a%20view%20of%20their%20surroundings%20and%20multiple%20escape%20routes.%20For%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20prioritized%20furniture%20that%20accounts%20for%20a%20cat's%20predator-prey%20instincts%20with%20large%20cutouts%20and%20more%20than%20one%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVentilation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20prioritized%20litter%20boxes%20with%20plenty%20of%20ventilation%2C%20so%20trapped%20ammonia%20particles%20don't%20irritate%20your%20cat's%20sensitive%20nose.%20We%20also%20considered%20options%20with%20odor-reducing%20features%2C%20like%20carbon%20filters.%20Our%20experts%20advise%20daily%20scooping%2C%20which%20they%20consider%20standard%20practice%20for%20any%20litter%20box%2C%20to%20prevent%20unpleasant%20odors%20from%20the%20hidden%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20searching%20for%20furniture%2C%20we%20prioritized%20seamless%20designs%20and%20water-resistant%20materials%20over%20porous%20materials.%20This%20helps%20ensure%20the%20furniture%20won't%20absorb%20urine%20and%20offensive%20odors.%20Plus%2C%20these%20designs%20are%20generally%20easier%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20assembly%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20selecting%20litter%20box%20enclosures%2C%20we%20opted%20for%20products%20with%20clear%20assembly%20instructions%2C%20manageable%20parts%2C%20and%20a%20user-friendly%20design.%20We%20prioritized%20options%20that%20provide%20step-by-step%20guidance%2C%20like%20Whisker's%20video%20instructions%2C%20and%20those%20that%20can%20easily%20snap%20together%2C%20like%20the%20Good%20Pet%20Stuff%20Hidden%20Litter%20Box%20planter.%20We%20also%20considered%20fully%20assembled%20options%2C%20like%20Qvelo's%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20experts%20recommend%20having%20one%20litter%20box%20per%20cat%2C%20plus%20one%20extra%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20enclosing%20all%20those%20litter%20boxes%20in%20furniture%20can%20add%20up%20quickly.%20So%2C%20we%20included%20furniture%20at%20a%20range%20of%20price%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257ae98bd-f964-40fd-89c7-358416b4746d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20litter%20box%20furniture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20select%20the%20best%20litter%20box%20furniture%2C%20we%20consulted%20two%20veterinarians%20and%20a%20certified%20feline%20training%20and%20behavior%20specialist%20(CFTBS).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Michelle%20Lugones%20is%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Best%20Friends%20Animal%20Society's%20New%20York%20Lifesaving%20Center%20and%20an%20associate%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20LaGuardia%20Community%20College's%20veterinary%20technology%20program.%20Lugones%20helped%20us%20understand%20the%20biological%20needs%20of%20a%20cat%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20proper%20litter%20box%20placement%20and%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolly%20DeVoss%20is%20a%20certified%20feline%20training%20and%20behavior%20specialist%20(CFTBS)%2C%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%2C%20and%20Fear%20Free%20certified%20trainer%20who%20specializes%20in%20using%20positive%20reinforcement%20to%20modify%20and%20prevent%20unwanted%20behaviors%20in%20cats.%20She%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20owner%20of%20Cat%20Behavior%20Solutions.%20DeVoss%20helped%20us%20understand%20what%20features%20make%20litter%20box%20furniture%20adaptable%20to%20a%20cat's%20needs%20and%20what%20features%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mark%20Freeman%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20community%20practice%20at%20Virginia-Maryland%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%20Freeman%20helped%20us%20understand%20how%20best%20humans%20and%20cats%20can%20cohabitate%20comfortability%2C%20which%20includes%20making%20compromises%20with%20litter%20box%20placement%20and%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20conducted%20extensive%20research%20to%20develop%20our%20selection%20criteria%20for%20the%20best%20litter%20box%20furniture.%20We%20then%20reviewed%20the%20options%20available%20at%20major%20online%20retailers%20to%20select%20our%20top%20choices%20in%2012%20different%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22461a5ddd-6feb-4eef-ae56-1afe79e81e43%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ELitter%20box%20furniture%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWill%20cats%20use%20litter%20box%20furniture%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20cats%20will%20use%20litter%20box%20furniture%20when%20the%20design%20appropriately%20meets%20their%20needs.%20When%20introducing%20the%20furniture%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Lugones%20advises%20against%20limiting%20your%20cat's%20access%20to%20an%20unenclosed%20litter%20box.%20Instead%2C%20provide%20a%20litter%20box%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20furniture%2C%20and%20let%20your%20cat%20choose%20which%20to%20use.%20Start%20by%20cleaning%20both%20boxes%20as%20needed%2C%20eventually%20cleaning%20the%20unenclosed%20box%20less%20often.%20Once%20your%20cat%20consistently%20uses%20the%20litter%20box%20inside%20the%20furniture%2C%20it's%20safe%20to%20remove%20the%20other%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20litter%20box%20furniture%20help%20with%20odors%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELitter%20box%20furniture%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20trap%20odors%2C%20which%20your%20cat%20probably%20dislikes%20just%20as%20much%20as%20you%20do.%20To%20prevent%20odors%2C%20opt%20for%20litter%20box%20furniture%20with%20adequate%20airflow%20and%20avoid%20using%20scented%20litter%2C%20which%20is%20too%20harsh%20for%20many%20casts.%20Lugones%20says%20the%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20litter%20box%20odors%20is%20by%20scooping%20daily%20and%20deep%20cleaning%20the%20box%20every%20two%20to%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhere%20should%20a%20cat's%20litter%20box%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20house%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20spot%20for%20a%20litter%20box%20is%20away%20from%20heavy%20foot%20traffic.%20Litter%20boxes%20should%20be%20spread%20throughout%20the%20home%20and%20not%20placed%20in%20rooms%20with%20loud%20appliances%2C%20like%20washing%20machines%20and%20dishwashers%2C%20DeVoss%20says.%20In%20multi-story%20homes%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20have%20a%20litter%20box%20on%20each%20floor.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20too%2C%20that%20while%20concealing%20a%20litter%20box%20from%20plain%20view%20is%20a%20major%20perk%20of%20litter%20box%20furniture%2C%20experts%20caution%20against%20hiding%20it%20so%20well%20that%20you%20forget%20to%20scoop.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can't%20see%20the%20litter%2C%20we%20might%20wait%20until%20we%20can%20smell%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20cleaned%2C%20and%20that's%20way%20too%20dirty%20for%20a%20cat's%20liking%2C%26quot%3B%20DeVoss%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20hidden%20litter%20boxes%20work%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFurniture%20that%20offers%20a%20way%20to%20disguise%20the%20litter%20box%20that%20can%20work%20well%20in%20small%20living%20spaces.%20These%20furniture%20pieces%20can%20blend%20in%20with%20your%20home%20decor%2C%20providing%20a%20functional%20space%20for%20the%20litter%20box%20while%20concealing%20its%20purpose.%20However%2C%20cats%20who%20feel%20insecure%20about%20resources%2C%20have%20conflict%20with%20other%20cats%20in%20the%20home%2C%20or%20see%20cats%20outside%20the%20window%20may%20not%20prefer%20an%20enclosed%20litter%20box%2C%20DeVoss%20says.%20This%20is%20because%20cats%20feel%20safer%20eliminating%20in%20the%20open%20where%20they%20can%20watch%20for%20threats%20and%20make%20a%20quick%20escape%20when%20necessary.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20too%2C%20that%20without%20proper%20ventilation%20and%20cleaning%2C%20litter%20box%20furniture%20can%20also%20worsen%20the%20box's%20smell%20%E2%80%94%20which%20neither%20you%20nor%20your%20cat%20will%20like.%20%26quot%3BA%20dislike%20for%20the%20box%20can%20result%20in%20inappropriate%20elimination%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20DeVoss%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20cats%20like%20litter%20box%20furniture%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cats%20might%20prefer%20using%20a%20hidden%20litter%20box%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20like%20hiding%20in%20enclosed%20spaces.%20Features%20like%20mesh%2C%20slots%2C%20grates%2C%20and%20multiple%20entrances%20can%20add%20light%20and%20visibility%20to%20the%20box%20and%20help%20cats%20feel%20more%20secure%20when%20using%20litter%20box%20furniture.%20Still%2C%20less%20confident%20cats%20or%20cats%20experiencing%20conflicts%20with%20other%20pets%20may%20prefer%20to%20use%20an%20open%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20hidden%20litter%20boxes%20good%20for%20cats%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20litter%20box%20furniture%20designed%20with%20a%20cat's%20needs%20in%20mind%20could%20benefit%20your%20cat%2C%20Freeman%20says.%20Appropriately-designed%20litter%20box%20furniture%20provides%20cats%20with%20a%20secure%20and%20private%20space%20while%20also%20allowing%20them%20to%20observe%20their%20surroundings.%20Some%20designs%20also%20provide%20lounging%20or%20resting%20areas%20for%20cats%20or%20function%20as%20tables%20or%20benches%20for%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20I%20get%20my%20cat%20to%20use%20litter%20box%20furniture%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20encourage%20your%20cat%20to%20use%20new%20litter%20box%20furniture%2C%20Lugones%20recommends%20placing%20it%20next%20to%20their%20current%20litter%20b