se%20the%20console's%20extra%20power%20in%20more%20deliberate%20ways.%20These%20enhancements%20can%20include%20better-optimized%20frame%20rates%20as%20well%20as%20upgraded%20ray%20tracing%20and%20other%20graphical%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20notably%2C%20PS5%20Pro-enhanced%20games%20have%20the%20option%20to%20use%20Sony's%20new%20AI-upscaling%20process%20called%20PlayStation%20Spectral%20Super%20Resolution%2C%20or%20PSSR.%20This%20process%20enables%20the%20system%20to%20create%20a%204K-quality%20image%20from%20a%20lower%20resolution%20while%20often%20holding%20a%20steady%2060%20FPS%20or%20higher.%20So%20far%2C%20Sony%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.playstation.com%2F2024%2F11%2F04%2Fps5-pro-50-enhanced-games-available-at-launch-november-7%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfirmed%20a%20little%20over%2050%20PS5%20Pro-enhanced%20titles%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20leverage%20features%20like%20PSSR%2C%20with%20more%20games%20being%20supported%20later.%20It's%20a%20good%20start%2C%20but%20there's%20definitely%20room%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8eaae95-fdc1-4a1b-b6fe-5dc2ce3c069d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22PS5%20Pro-enhanced%20performance%5C%22%3EPS5%20Pro-enhanced%20games%20look%20prettier%20and%20run%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222735%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Final%20Fantasy%20VII%20running%20on%20a%20PS5%20Pro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761a26a4ea3c98ea3e4e8aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222051%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinal%20Fantasy%20VII%20Rebirth%20has%20a%20new%20Versatility%20mode%20on%20PS5%20Pro%20which%20enables%20sharp%20and%20smooth%20gameplay.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Yang%2FSquare%20Enix%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20a%20mix%20of%20first-%20and%20third-party%20PS5%20Pro-enhanced%20games%20to%20see%20how%20these%20new%20features%20stack%20up.%20I%20downloaded