2%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761a2c16c531c315b88c1a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarvel's%20Spider-Man%202%20looks%20and%20plays%20fantastic%20using%20the%20new%20Performance%20Pro%20mode.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Yang%2FInsomniac%20Games%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMarvel's%20Spider-Man%202%20is%20also%20a%20good%20showcase%20of%20the%20PS5%20Pro.%20The%20game%20offers%20new%20Performance%20Pro%20and%20Fidelity%20Pro%20modes%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20prioritizing%20visual%20quality%20and%20the%20former%20focusing%20on%20holding%20a%20steady%20frame%20rate.%20Both%20are%20fantastic%2C%20but%20Performance%20Pro%20is%20the%20clear%20winner%20for%20me.%20The%20high%20frame%20rate%20and%20sharp%20resolution%20gave%20me%20a%20huge%20rush%20while%20swinging%20at%20blisteringly%20fast%20speeds%20through%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Demon's%20Souls%20now%20has%20a%20mode%20called%20PS5%20Pro.%20I%20switched%20between%20the%20standard%20PS5's%20Performance%20and%20Cinematic%20modes%20to%20compare.%20Similar%20to%20Final%20Fantasy%20VII%20Rebirth's%20Versatility%20mode%2C%20I%20could%20see%20a%20solid%20improvement.%20In%20the%20old%20Cinematic%20mode%2C%20rotating%20the%20camera%20caused%20a%20nauseating%20motion%20blur%20effect%20due%20to%20the%20lower%20frame%20rate%2C%20while%20Performance%20mode%20would%20alleviate%20that%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20some%20visual%20fidelity.%20The%20PS5%20Pro%20mode%20makes%20Demon's%20Souls%20look%20sharper%20while%20completely%20diminishing%20the%20distracting%20motion%20blur.%20It's%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Demon's%20Souls%20running%20on%20a%20PS5%20Pro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761a30cd610a4acda56b12a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemon's%20Souls%20is%20another%20title%20that%20benefits%20from%20a%20PS5%20Pro%20mode%20that%20offers%20high%20frame%20rates%20without%20sacrificing%20graphical%20fidelity.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Yang%2FSony%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tested%20Stellar%20Blade%2C%20which%20received%20two%20new%20display%20modes%20on%20the%20PS5%20Pro%3A%20Pro%20and%20Pro%20Max.%20Of%20the%20games%20I%20tested%2C%20Stellar%20Blade%20was%20the%20most%20inconsistent%20in%20terms%20of%20performance.%20Pro%20mode%20kept%2060%20FPS%20while%20utilizing%20PSSR%20to%20produce%20great%20image%20quality.%20However%2C%20the%20Pro%20Max%20mode%20was%20confusing.%20The%20settings%20menu%20states%20that%20it%20provides%20a%20higher%20frame%20rate%20while%20also%20prioritizing%20resolution%2C%20but%20my%20experience%20was%20the%20opposite.%20When%20in%20combat%2C%20the%20frames%20drop%20a%20bit%20when%20set%20to%20Pro%20Max%20mode.%20That%20wasn't%20the%20case%20in%20Pro%20mode.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20Pro%20mode%20was%20better%20since%20it%20was%20more%20consistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20PS5%20Pro-enhanced%20game%20I%20tested%20was%20Resident%20Evil%204%20Remake.%20The%20PS5%20Pro%20allows%20you%20to%20unlock%20the%20game's%20frame%20rate%2C%20enabling%20it%20to%20run%20above%2060%20FPS%20while%20still%20offering%20a%20high%20resolution%2C%20ray-tracing%2C%20and%20other%20advanced%20visual%20options.%20Alternatively%2C%20you%20can%20disable%20the%20advanced%20graphics%20features%20to%20boost%20the%20game%20to%20nearly%20100%20FPS%2C%20which%20is%20very%20helpful%20in%20such%20an%20action-heavy%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22335e4896-4be1-4987-91bc-8786ea02ef64%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Can%20it%20improve%20PS4%20games%3F%5C%22%3ESome%20PS4%20games%20also%20look%20improved%2C%20but%20the%20upgrade%20is%20subtle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Bloodborne%20on%20PS4.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761c5f41d90e3bcf31d692c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20PS5%20Pro%20can%20improve%20the%20image%20quality%20of%20some%20PS4%20games%2C%20like%20Bloodborne.%3Cp%3EAmazon%2FSony%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20PS5%20games%2C%20the%20PS5%20Pro%20can%20also%20enhance%20PS4%20games%20when%20you%20enable%20a%20toggle%20in%20the%20system%20settings%20menu%20called%20%26quot%3BEnhance%20Image%20Quality%20for%20PS4%20Games.%26quot%3B%20This%20feature%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20specifically%20added%20by%20a%20developer%20and%20instead%20simply%20uses%20the%20Pro's%20increased%20power%20to%20offer%20a%20bump%20in%20image%20clarity.%20Among%20the%20games%20I%20tested%20were%20Bloodborne%2C%20Nier%3A%20Automata%2C%20and%20Yakuza%200.%20While%20Bloodborne's%20gothic%20environments%20looked%20a%20bit%20sharper%2C%20its%20frame%20rate%20was%20still%20locked%20at%2030%20FPS.%20Nier%3A%20Automata%20and%20Yakuza%200%20felt%20smooth%20and%20responsive%2C%20but%20that%20was%20mostly%20because%20they%20were%20already%20optimized%20well%20for%20the%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20notes%20for%20this%20feature%20say%20it%20only%20applies%20to%20%26quot%3Bsome%20games%26quot%3B%20but%20don't%20mention%20specifically%20which%20ones.%20They%20also%20mention%20turning%20the%20feature%20off%20if%20you%20experience%20unexpected%20issues.%20While%20this%20option%20is%20nice%20to%20have%2C%20its%20benefits%20have%20been%20negligible%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223288f65f-8e97-4073-a55a-5168cc52df79%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20PS5%20Pro%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20PS5%20Pro%20controller%20resting%20horizontally%20on%20a%20table%20with%20a%20DualSense%20controller.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20s