20sustainability%20of%20the%20museum%2C%26quot%3B%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum%20director%20Kevin%20Cullen%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20the%20Sub%20BnB%20starts%20at%20%24500%20per%20night%2C%20plus%20a%20%24100%20cleaning%20fee%20and%20an%20%2485%20Airbnb%20service%20fee%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%24685.%20Business%20Insider%20paid%20a%20discounted%20media%20rate%20of%20%24200%20to%20report%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20earned%20from%20Sub%20Bnb%20stays%20help%20support%20the%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20by%20staying%20there%2C%20you%20get%20that%20authentic%20experience%2C%20but%20you're%20also%20supporting%20preservation%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Cullen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20I%20visited%20the%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum%20for%20an%20overnight%20stay%20on%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20accompanied%20by%20my%20dad%2C%20a%20maritime%20enthusiast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20spend%20a%20night%20on%20a%20World%20War%20II%20submarine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20USS%20Cobia%20was%20visible%20from%20the%20parking%20lot%20when%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum%20for%20our%20submarine%20stay.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20USS%20Cobia%20visible%20from%20the%20parking%20lot%20of%20the%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757340c91c1cc343d4767b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USS%20Cobia.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20Cobia%20was%20docked%20outside%20the%20museum%20in%20the%20Manitowoc%20River.%20The%20freshwater%20river%20has%20helped%20preserve%20the%20submarine%20over%20the%20years%20since%20it's%20less%20corrosive%20than%20saltwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInside%20the%20museum%2C%20we%20were%20greeted%20by%20Mark%20Becker%2C%20a%20US%20Navy%20submarine%20veteran%20and%20museum%20volunteer%20who%20served%20as%20our%20tour%20guide.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Becker.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67570e0ea57635a3d24d18ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Becker.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecker%20served%20on%20the%20USS%20Silversides%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBecker%20took%20us%20outside%20for%20our%20first%20proper%20look%20at%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20USS%20Cobia%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67571e848fbb2783ed309536%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USS%20Cobia%20at%20night.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20Cobia%20sank%2013%20ships%20during%20its%20six%20patrols%20in%20World%20War%20II%2C%20earning%20four%20battle%20stars.%20The%20submarine%20also%20rescued%20seven%20downed%20American%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20war%2C%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20was%20brought%20to%20Manitowoc%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20memorial%20for%20submariners.%20The%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum%20acquired%20it%20in%201986.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20became%20a%20National%20Historic%20Landmark%20and%20was%20added%20to%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20submarine%20to%20grace%20the%20shores%20of%20Manitowoc.%20The%20Manitowoc%20Shipbuilding%20Company%2C%20which%20was%20located%20just%20miles%20from%20the%20museum%2C%20built%2028%20submarines%20during%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStanding%20on%20the%20deck%2C%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20size%20of%20the%20submarine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20deck%20of%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675733a8dc8b666017f20ecd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20deck%20of%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20at%20night.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecker%20told%20us%20that%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20actually%20spent%20most%20of%20her%20patrols%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20water%2C%20not%20underwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCobia%20is%20basically%20a%20gunboat%20that%20can%20submerge%20if%20she%20has%20to%2C%20not%20like%20a%20true%20submarine%20like%20I%20was%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCobia%20was%20better%20on%20the%20surface.%20Faster%2C%20more%20maneuverable%2C%20and%20way%20more%20firepower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20smell%20of%20diesel%20fuel%20became%20stronger%20as%20I%20walked%20down%20a%20set%20of%20stairs%20into%20the%20submarine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20to%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67570e0e4adc4cc134354e99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20USS%20Cobia.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stairs%20didn't%20exist%20during%20the%20USS%20Cobia's%20wartime%20service.%20Sailors%20used%20ladders%20to%20enter%20and%20exit%20the%20sub%20through%20narrow%20hatches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBecker%20said%20we%20were%20free%20to%20sleep%20in%20any%20of%20the%20bunks%20on%20the%20USS%20Cobia%20that%20we%20saw%20along%20the%20tour.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20forward%20torpedo%20room%20on%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%2