0if%20one%20forgot%20to%20duck.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Talia%20Lakritz%20on%20board%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67571eeb4adc4cc134355a2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221357%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20board%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20doorways%20that%20could%20be%20walked%20through%2C%20the%20hatches%20required%20me%20to%20duck%20and%20climb%20through%20the%20small%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecker%20said%20that%20during%20his%20submarine%20service%20in%20the%20Navy%2C%20he%20once%20hit%20his%20head%20while%20running%20through%20the%20ship%20after%20a%20call%20rang%20out%20for%20crew%20members%20to%20report%20to%20their%20battle%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20duck%20far%20enough%2C%20and%2C%20pow%2C%20I%20hit%20my%20head%20at%20the%20top%20of%20that%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20damn%20near%20knocked%20myself%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20perk%20of%20staying%20on%20the%20submarine%20overnight%20was%20the%20personalized%20tour%2C%20which%20included%20spaces%20not%20usually%20open%20to%20the%20public%20like%20the%20pump%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shaft%20on%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67570e0e4adc4cc134354e98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20shaft%20on%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20control%20room%2C%20which%20contained%20the%20ship's%20navigational%20equipment%20and%20controls%2C%20Becker%20opened%20a%20hatch%20in%20the%20floor%20that%20led%20to%20the%20pump%20room.%20I%20climbed%20down%20the%20ladder%20to%20take%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ET