n%20Maritime%20Museum%20after%20hours.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20I%20watched%20%26quot%3BNight%20at%20the%20Museum%2C%26quot%3B%20a%202006%20film%20in%20which%20exhibits%20at%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20come%20alive%20at%20night%2C%20I've%20wondered%20what%20it%20would%20be%20like%20to%20visit%20a%20museum%20after%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20my%20%26quot%3BNight%20at%20the%20Museum%26quot%3B%20dreams%20came%20true%20at%20the%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum.%20We%20were%20given%20free%20rein%20to%20wander%20as%20we%20pleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20the%20museum%20at%20night%20did%20feel%20different%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20way%20that%20watching%20a%20scary%20movie%20in%20the%20dark%20adds%20a%20certain%20gravitas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20had%20the%20entire%20museum%20to%20ourselves%2C%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20take%20our%20time%20looking%20through%20the%20exhibits.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exhibits%20at%20the%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676087c5d0de6a4f27d3363d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExhibits%20at%20the%20Wisconsin%20Maritime%20Museum.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20particularly%20enjoyed%20the%20exhibits%20about%20shipwreck%20artifacts%20discovered%20off%20the%20coasts%20of%20Wisconsin%20and%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Manitowoc%20Shipbuilding%20Company.%20Even%20though%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20of%20the%20extent%20of%20its%20maritime%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20my%20bunk%20that%20night%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20all%20of%20the%20soldiers%20who%20left%20their%20families%20and%20homes%20to%20spend%20months%20on%20board%20the%20USS%20Cobia.%3Cfigure%3E%3C