%2C%20the%20same%20Bhujbal%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20rear%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20take%20some%20action%2C%20though%20he%20has%20left%20everyone%20guessing%20on%20what%20it%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20%26quot%3BJaha%20nahi%20chaina%2C%20waha%20nahi%20rehna%20(no%20staying%20where%20there%20is%20no%20peace)%26quot%3B%20comment%20has%20led%20to%20speculation%20that%20he%20might%20join%20the%20BJP%20or%20float%20his%20own%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20has%20made%20clear%20is%20that%20he%20is%20upset%20with%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20his%20party%20--%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Praful%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20never%20about%20inclusion%20in%20the%20cabinet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20while%20explaining%20how%20he%20was%20left%20out%20of%20the%20council%20of%20ministers%20despite%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20clearing%20his%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20I%20have%20been%20treated%20is%20objectionable.%20We%20just%20have%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20orders%20of%20three%20persons.%20There%20is%20no%20participation%20at%20all.%20We%20have%20no%20clue%20what%20is%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NCP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal's%20supporters%20within%20the%20NCP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20hit%20the%20streets.%20Protests%20were%20held%20in%20Pune%20and%20outside%20the%20bungalow%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20Baramati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20ministers%20Bhujbal%20and%20Dilip%20Walse%20Patil%20of%20the%20NCP%20and%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%20and%20Vijaykumar%20Gavit%20of%20the%20BJP%20are%20among%20the%20prominent%20leaders%20who%20didn't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20state%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734460140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncps-chhagan-bhujbal-out-of-cabinet-opposition-lends-a-sho