ians%20of%20Bangladesh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Congress%20MPs%20led%20by%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20also%20staged%20a%20protest%20on%20the%20Parliament%20premises%20demanding%20justice%20for%20Hindus%20and%20Christians%20facing%20atrocities%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20a%20day%20after%20she%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20by%20carrying%20a%20handbag%20with%20'Palestine'%20emblazoned%20on%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734460140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnacboc1g_priyanka-gandhi-palestine_625x300_17_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthrowing-youths-into-war-zone-priyanka-gandhi-slams-up-cm-over-israel-remarks-7272118%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20throwing%20youths%20into%20the%20war%20zone%20in%20Israel%20for%20%26quot%3Bemployment%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20an%20achievement%20but%20a%20matter%20of%20shame.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthrowing-youths-into-war-zone-priyanka-gandhi-slams-up-cm-over-israel-remarks-7272118%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20erupts%20after%20lightning%20strike%20ruptures%20gas%20line%20in%20Tennessee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734460109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5ac5%2Flive%2Fd5c8d500-bca1-11ef-aff0-072ce821b6ab.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcy53p0xvv7do%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20damaged%20pipeline%20sparked%20a%20massive%20fire%20prompting%20road%20closures%20and%20emergenc