oung%20girls%20and%20women%20who%20were%20already%20frustrated%20with%20restrictions%20imposed%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20was%20also%20criticised%20by%20Masoumeh%20Ebtekar%2C%20a%20former%20vice-president%20for%20women%20and%20family%20affairs%2C%20who%20called%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Ban%20indictment%20of%20half%20the%20Iranian%20population%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hijab%20discourse%20has%20always%20been%20in%20the%20picture%20but%20it%20was%20reinforced%20more%20so%20when%20a%20woman%2C%20Parastoo%20Ahmadi%2C%20was%20arrested%20after%20she%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20herself%20singing%20on%20YouTube%20without%20a%20hijab%2C%20in%20a%20sleeveless%20dress%2C%20with%20her%20hair%20down%20accompanied%20by%20four%20male%20musicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20Parastoo%2C%20a%20girl%20who%20wants%20to%20sing%20for%20the%20people%20I%20love.%20This%20is%20a%20right%20I%20could%20not%20ignore%3B%20singing%20for%20the%20land%20I%20love%20passionately%26quot%3B%2C%20read%20the%20caption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20she%20was%20arrested%20along%20with%20her%20band%20members%20but%20was%20released%20a%20day%20later%20after%20the%20arrest%20received%20widespread%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hijab%20controversy%20has%20been%20ongoing%20since%202022%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20death%20of%20Mahsa%20%26quot%3BZhina%26quot%3B%20Amini%2C%20who%20died%20in%20police%20custody%20after%20violating%20the%20dress%20code.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20her%20death%2C%20women%20have%20challenged%20the%20government%20and%20defied%20hijab%20rules.%20Younger%20people%20in%20Iran%20appear%20fearless%20and%20defying%20such%20laws%20despite%20the%20restrictions%20and%20pressure%20from%20factions%20close%20to%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0mv83m4z7vo%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20last%20week%2C%20more%20than%20300%20Iranian%20rights%20activists%2C%20writers%20and%20journalists%20publicly%20condemned%20the%20new%20hijab%20law%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Billegitimate%20and%20unenforceable%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20Pezeshkian%20to%20honour%20his%20campaign%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20pause%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law%20shows%20that%20the%20government%20is%20apprehensive%20of%20the%20protests%20that%20might%20set%20off%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20seen%20two%20years%20ago.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734455940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fkhfrha6o_hijab-law-istock_625x300_17_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-holds-back-hijab-law-after-widespread-condemnation-7271950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hijab%20discourse%20was%20reinforced%20more%20so%20when%20a%20woman%2C%20Parastoo%20Ahmadi%2C%20was%20arrested%20after%20she%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20herself%20singing%20on%20YouTube%20with%20her%20hair%20down%20without%20a%20hijab%2C%20in%20a%20sleeveless%20dress%2C%20with%20four%20male%20musicians%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-holds-back-hijab-law-after-widespread-condemnation-7271950%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cyclone%20kills%20dozens%20in%20Mozambique%20after%20ravaging%20French%20territory%20Mayotte%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734455450000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F76d9%2Flive%2F13eecba0-bc7f-11ef-9e94-492e454c4f8c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc30nz8dr051o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mozambican%20authorities%20have%20called%20Chido%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20intense%20st