ed%20as%20part%20of%20changes%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Transaction%20of%20Business%20Rules%20(TBR)%20were%20made%20in%20July%2C%20two%20months%20before%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%20They%20widened%20some%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20and%20had%20attracted%20criticism%20from%20Mr%20Abdullah%20at%20the%20time%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20indicator%20that%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20This%20is%20why%20a%20firm%20commitment%20laying%20out%20the%20timeline%20for%20restoration%20of%20full%2C%20undiluted%20statehood%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20these%20elections.%20The%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20deserved%20better%20than%20a%20powerless%2C%20rubber%20stamp%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20will%20have%20to%20beg%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20to%20get%20his%2Fher%20peon%20appointed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20had%20been%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20stating%20that%20he%20wants%20good%20relations%20with%20the%20Centre%20ahead%20of%20his%20oath%20ceremony%20in%20October%2C%20there%20has%20been%20friction%20between%20the%20National%20Conference%20leader%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20on%20several%20occasions.%20The%20transfer%20of%20some%20state%20administrative%20officers%20is%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20friction%20between%20the%20Chief%20Minister-led%20administration%20and%20the%20office%20of%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20is%20quite%20evident.%20Often%2C%20important%20files%20are%20delayed%20and%20transfers%20are%20made%20without%20even%20informing%20the%20chief%20minister.%20The%20recent%20transfer%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Administrative%20Service%20(JKAS)%20officers%20and%20extensions%20given%20to%20some%20others%20are%20now%20the%20latest%20point%20of%20difference%20between%20Mr%20Abdullah%20and%20Mr%20Sinha%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20MLAs%20have%20also%20raised%20concerns%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20that%20most%20basic%20public%20issues%20have%20remained%20unresolved%20and%20officers%20from%20the%20JKAS%20do%20not%20pay%20any%20heed%20to%20their%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20business%20and%20conduct%20rules%2C%20we%20have%20another%20power%20centre%20(lieutenant%20governor)%20and%20this%20needs%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20CPM%20MLA%20Mohamad%20Yousuf%20Tarigami%20told%20NDTV.%20He%20said%20this%20is%20why%20he%20had%20stated%20in%20the%20Assembly%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20House%20where%20the%20House%20also%20does%20not%20know%20what%20it%20can%20or%20cannot%20legislate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20bureaucrat%2C%20however%2C%20said%20no%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20TBR%20unless%20amendments%20are%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20was%20given%20powers%20to%20take%20decisions%20as%20per%20law%20and%20he%20is%20doing%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bureaucrat%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmendments%20Soon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20a%20draft%20of%20an%20amended%20TBR%2C%20giving%20more%20clarity%20on%20the%20distribution%20of%20powers%2C%20has%20already%20been%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20cleared%2C%20the%20business%20rules%20will%20help%20streamline%20the%20governance%20process%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20ensuring%20greater%20efficiency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20administration.%20The%20rules%20will%20also%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20providing%20a%20clear%20legal%20and%20operational%20structure%20to%20the%20governance%20model%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20line%20with%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20made%20in%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20gave%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20tussle%20between%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20given%20more%20ammunition%20to%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20Congress%2C%20PDP%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20which%20have%20been%20pushing%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20for%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Wednesday's%20meeting%20will%20be%20the%20second%20%C2%A0between%20Mr%20Abdullah%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20since%20the%20National%20Conference%20leader%20took%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734454860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0ucpmu9o_omar-abdullah-meets-amit-shah-_625x300_23_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-lieutenant-governor-manoj-sinha-statehood-lt-governors-powers-in-focus-as-omar-abdullah-amit-shah-meet-tomorrow-7271812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20meets%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20will%20not%20be%20the%20only%20item%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20agenda%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-lieutenant-governor-manoj-sinha-statehood-lt-governors-powers-in-focus-as-omar-abdullah-amit-shah-meet-tomorrow-7271812%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Bipasha%20spoke%20about%20breakup%20with%20John%20Abraham%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734454664000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116408039%2Cimgsize-32090.cms%22%2C%22originID%