s%20the%20result%3F%20What%20was%20the%20aim%20of%20making%20the%20changes%3F%20Was%20it%20to%20strengthen%20democracy%20or%20stay%20in%20power%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20MP%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20has%20been%20carrying%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20with%20him%20to%20various%20events%20since%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20He%20also%20took%20oath%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20on%20the%20foundational%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20carried%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20been%20exposed%20as%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bblank%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20blank%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20biggest%20fraud%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20termed%20the%20claims%20of%20%26quot%3BConstitution%20in%20danger%26quot%3B%20a%20political%20gimmick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20treated%20the%20Constitution%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bprivate%20fiefdom%26quot%3B%20of%20one%20family%20and%20%26quot%3Bplayed%20fraud%26quot%3B%20with%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2075%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20played%20fraud%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Constitution...%20They%20(Nehru-Gandhi%20family)%20considered%20not%20just%20the%20party%20as%20their%20private%20property%2C%20but%20also%20treated%20the%20Constitution%20as%20their%20'private%20fiefdom'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20insertion%20of%20Article%2035A%20without%20parliamentary%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734451860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F1j87nid8_amit-shah-rahul-gandhi-split_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F54-year-old-young-leade