While%20the%20world%20is%20focused%20on%20central%20and%20west%20Asia%20and%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20West%20vis-a-vis%20the%20wars%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Europe%2C%20India%20has%20been%20looking%20and%20acting%20eastward%20with%20its%20Act%20East%20policy.%20Besides%20boosting%20its%20ties%20with%20Southeast%20Asian%20nations%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20working%20silently%20and%20cautiously%20towards%20its%20policy%20in%20the%20Korean%20peninsula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20functions%20with%20a%20great%20degree%20of%20opacity%2C%20which%20in%20turn%2C%20leads%20New%20Delhi%20to%20also%20maintain%20its%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Pyongyang%20in%20the%20shadows%2C%20unnoticed%20and%20silent%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202021%2C%20India%20quietly%20shut%20its%20embassy%20in%20Pyongyang%20and%20Ambassador%20Atul%20Malhari%20Gotsurve%20along%20with%20the%20entire%20staff%20returned%20to%20New%20Delhi%20via%20Moscow.%20Though%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20never%20officially%20declared%20the%20embassy%20'closed'%2C%20when%20asked%20by%20journalists%20why%20the%20entire%20staff%20was%20called%20back%2C%20it%20said%20the%20step%20was%20taken%20due%20to%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20went%20by%20with%20no%20update%20on%20the%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20Pyongyang%2C%20and%20fourteen%20months%20ago%2C%20Mr%20Gotsurve%20was%20given%20a%20new%20posting%20as%20Ambassador%20to%20Mongolia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20year%20went%20by%2C%20and%20then%20suddenly%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20India%20decided%20to%20resume%20normal%20operations%20at%20its%20embassy%20in%20Pyongyang.%20Within%20days%20a%20team%20comprising%20technical%20staff%20and%20diplomatic%20personnel%20were%20dispatched%20for%20North%20Korea.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fcomment%2Frevival-of-indias-north-korean-mission-reflects-strategic-shift%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20staff%20has%20already%20reached%20Pyongyang%20and%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20making%20the%20mission%20fully%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%2C%20now%20shut%20for%20more%20than%20three-and-a-half%20years%2C%20needs%20to%20first%20undergo%20a%20thorough%20check.%20North%20Korea%2C%20infamous%20for%20its%20suspicious%20intelligence-gathering%20techniques%2C%20would%20mean%20the%20staff%20must%20first%20debug%20the%20entire%20embassy%20building.%20This%2C%20and%20the%20delays%20expected%20from%20North%20Korea's%20bureaucracy%2C%20means%20that%20a%20new%20Ambassador%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team%20might%20be%20several%20months%20away%20from%20joining%20the%20initial%20staff%20sent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENORTH%20KOREA'S%20GROWING%20IMPACT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea's%20strategic%20importance%20today%20is%20significantly%20more%20than%20it%20was%20four%20years%20ago%20-%20not%20just%20for%20India%20and%20Asia%2C%20but%20for%20the%20West%20too.%20Militarily%2C%20North%20Korea%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing%20its%20nuclear%20arsenal%20while%20also%20rapidly%20working%20on%20technology%20such%20as%20hypersonic%20missiles%2C%20tactical%20weapons%2C%20short%2C%20medium%20and%20long-range%20missiles%2C%20among%20others.%20For%20India%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20be%20present%20in%20Pyongyang%20and%20establish%20ties%20such%2C%20that%20such%20technology%20does%20not%20make%20its%20way%20to%20Pakistan%20or%20its%20rouge%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20North%20Korea%20has%20also%20deepened%20its%20ties%20with%20Russia%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Iran%20-%20a%20growing%20alliance%20in%20Asia%20which%20many%20see%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20the%20Quad%20-%20a%20security%20and%20trade%20grouping%20comprising%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Australia.%20This%2