s%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcyclone-chido-before-and-after-pictures-show-devastating-storms-damage-to-mayotte-13275377%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcyclone-chido-before-and-after-pictures-show-devastating-storms-damage-to-mayotte-13275377%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WTC%20Final%20Qualification%20Scenarios%20For%20All%20Teams%20And%20Updated%20Points%20Table%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%202023-25%20is%20reaching%20its%20business%20end.%20A%20three-match%20Test%20series%20between%20New%20Zealand%20and%20England%20concluded%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20both%20teams%20out%20of%20contention%20for%20the%20title%20clash%20at%20Lord's%20next%20year.%20The%20state%20of%20play%20currently%20sees%20India%20and%20Australia%2C%20the%20last%20year's%20finalists%2C%20fighting%20it%20out%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20finals%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20while%20South%20Africa%20await%20Pakistan%20challenge%20at%20home.%20Here%20is%20the%20updated%20World%20Test%20Championship%20points%20table%20after%20New%20Zealand's%20win%20over%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fko0jla98_pt_625x300_17_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20brief%20stint%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%202023-25%20World%20Test%20Championship%20standings%20lasted%20just%20over%20a%20day%2C%20as%20South%20Africa%20overtook%20them%20with%20a%20hard-earned%20victory%20over%20Sri%20Lanka%20by%20109%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Proteas%20had%20to%20dig%20deep%2C%20but%20a%20standout%20all-round%20performance%20helped%20them%20secure%20the%20win%2C%20placing%20them%20as%20the%20front-runners%20for%20the%20WTC25%20Final%20at%20Lord's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20England's%20win%20over%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Christchurch%20in%20the%20first%20Test%2C%20both%20sides%20were%20penalised%20three%20WTC%20points%20for%20maintaining%20a%20slow%20over-rate%20and%20the%20Black%20Caps%20dropped%20to%20the%20fifth%20place%20in%20the%20standings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand's%20chances%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20summit%20clash%20took%20a%20significant%20hit%20after%20yet%20another%20dominating%20performance%20by%20England%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Wellington.%20New%20Zealand%20won%20the%20final%20Test%20by%20423%20runs%20and%20both%20teams%20finished%20their%20WTC25%20campaign%20with%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20series%20at%20fourth%20and%20sixth%20spots%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESouth%20Africa%20-%2063.33%20per%20cent%20of%20possible%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20Pakistan%20(home%2C%20two%20Tests)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBest%20Possible%20Finish%3A%2069.44%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarrying%20on%20the%20form%20from%20their%20impressive%20series%20win%20over%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20sub-continent%2C%20South%20Africa%20whitewashed%20Sri%20Lanka%202-0%20at%20home.%20This%20dominant%20performance%20has%20propelled%20them%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20standings%2C%20surpassing%20Australia%2C%20as%20per%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20two%20home%20games%20against%20Pakistan%20are%20extremely%20important%20for%20South%20Africa%2C%20for%20if%20they%20continue%20this%20winning%20run%2C%20they%20will%20be%20safely%20placed%20to%20make%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20irrespective%20of%20how%20the%20other%20sides%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAustralia%20-%2060.71%20per%20cent%20of%20possible%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20India%20(home%2C%20three%20Tests)%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20(away%2C%20two%20Tests)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBest%20possible%20finish%3A%2071.05%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20closely%20fought%20contest%20between%20Australia%20and%20India%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20top%20two%20of%20the%20WTC25%20standings.%20The%20reigning%20World%20Test%20Championship%20winners%20Australia%2C%20who%20had%20regained%20the%20top%20spot%20after%20India's%20series%20loss%20to%20New%20Zealand%2C%20slipped%20when%20they%20lost%20in%20Perth%20with%20India%20reaching%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa's%20win%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20pushed%20them%20down%20to%20No.3.%20However%2C%20a%20dominant%20win%20in%20the%20pink-ball%20Test%20in%20Adelaide%20propelled%20them%20to%20the%20top%20once%20again%2C%20albeit%20only%20temporarily%20as%20the%20Proteas%20surged%20ahead%20to%20claim%20the%20No.1%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20series%20now%20tied%20at%201-1%2C%20Australia%20are%20in%20a%20strong%20position%20for%20a%20top-two%20finish.%20They%20will%20also%20tour%20Sri%20Lanka%20next%20year%20for%20an%20additional%20two%20Tests%2C%20meaning%20they%20could%20theoretically%20draw%202-2%20with%20India%20and%20stay%20in%20contention%20for%20a%20place%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20-%2057.29%20per%20cent%20of%20possible%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20Australia%20(away%2C%20three%20Tests)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBest%20possible%20finish%3A%2064.04%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20unprecedented%203-0%20series%20whitewash%20at%20home%20in%20October%20against%20New%20Zealand%20which%20pushed%20them%20down%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20WTC%20table%2C%20India%20bounced%20back%20in%20the%20race%20for%20Lord's%20with%20a%20comprehensive%20win%20against%20Australia%20in%20Perth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20all-round%20display%20from%20the%20batters%20and%20the%20bowlers%20in%20Perth%20has%20rekindled%20India's%20hopes%20for%20a%20third%20straight