maining%20matches%3A%20Australia%20(home%2C%20two%20Tests)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBest%20Possible%20Finish%3A%2053.85%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20head-turning%20victory%20over%20England%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20away%20followed%20by%20a%202-0%20whitewash%20of%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20Sri%20Lanka's%20recent%20Test%20returns%2C%20and%20the%20Island%20nation%20went%20to%20South%20Africa%20confidently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%202-0%20series%20whitewash%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Proteas%20has%20significantly%20damaged%20Sri%20Lanka's%20chances%20of%20reaching%20the%20WTC25%20Final%2C%20leaving%20them%20needing%20several%20results%20to%20go%20their%20way%20for%20any%20hope%20of%20qualification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEngland%20-%2043.18%20per%20cent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20rampant%20home%20season%20had%20sparked%20some%20hopes%20for%20England%2C%20consecutive%20losses%20in%20Pakistan%20saw%20them%20drop%20out%20of%20contention%20for%20a%20spot%20at%20next%20year's%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20began%20their%20final%20outing%20in%20the%20WTC%2C%20a%20three-match%20series%20against%20the%20Black%20Caps%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20November%20on%20a%20positive%20note%20with%20an%20eight-wicket%20win.%20And%20then%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20big%20323-win%20in%20the%20second%20Test%2C%20thereby%20taking%20an%20unassailable%202-0%20lead%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20did%20not%20do%20well%20in%20the%20final%20Test%20and%20suffered%20a%20massive%20423-run%20loss%2C%20ending%20sixth%20on%20the%20WTC25%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPakistan%20-%2033.33%20per%20cent%20of%20possible%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20South%20Africa%20(away%2C%20two%20Tests)%2C%20West%20Indies%20(home%2C%20two%20Tests)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBest%20Possible%20Finish%3A%2052.38%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20won%20back-to-back%20Tests%20under%20the%20watchful%20eye%20of%20new%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jason%20Gillespie%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F203-jason-gillespie-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJason%20Gillespie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20remain%20out%20of%20contention%20of%20reaching%20the%20final%20with%20a%20total%20of%20six%20teams%20ahead%20of%20them%20on%20the%20standings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pakistan%20could%20still%20win%20their%20remaining%20four%20Tests%20and%20finish%20with%20a%20percentage%20as%20high%20as%2052.38%20per%20cent%2C%20this%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20enough%20to%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20two%20places%20on%20the%20standings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20next%20play%20South%20Africa%20at%20the%20end%20of%20December%20and%20then%20will%20welcome%20West%20Indies%20home%20for%20two%20Tests%20in%20January%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBangladesh%20-%2031.25%20per%20cent%20of%20possible%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20Nil%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBest%20Possible%20Finish%3A%2031.25%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Asian%20side%20finished%20their%20campaign%20on%20a%20high%20with%20an%20impressive%20101-run%20victory%20over%20the%20West%20Indies%20that%20helped%20them%20off%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20standings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20has%20been%20a%20relatively%20disappointing%20cycle%20for%20Bangladesh%2C%20they%20will%20be%20buoyed%20by%20the%20fact%20they%20won%20three%20Test%20matches%20away%20from%20home%20that%20including%20a%20series%20sweep%20over%20Pakistan%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20gives%20Bangladesh%20some%20hope%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%20though%20they%20will%20want%20to%20find%20some%20more%20consistent%20results%20on%20home%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20Indies%20-%2024.24%20per%20cent%20of%20possible%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%