ifferently%20mapped.%20The%20approach%20was%20entirely%20new%20and%20much%20deeper%20than%20the%20last%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreeja%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20A%20N%20Yellappa%20Reddy%2C%20a%20renowned%20environmentalist%20and%20former%20IFS%20officer%2C%20would%20tell%20the%20students%2C%20%E2%80%9CWater%20needs%20space%20to%20walk%2C%20crawl%2C%20jump%2C%20hop%2C%20and%20trickle%20in%20the%20city.%20Today%2C%20it%20only%20runs%3B%20and%20it%20runs%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20further%20point%20out%20that%2095%25%20of%20water%20in%20Bengaluru%20now%20runs%20off%2C%20a%20stark%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%2015-20%25%20just%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20Sreeja%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20ground%20was%20not%20paved%2C%20and%20construction%20materials%20were%20permeable.%20With%20urbanisation%2C%20however%2C%20a%20concrete%20jungle%20has%20emerged%2C%20leaving%20no%20space%20for%20water%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20will%20the%20water%20go%2C%20then%3F%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Reddy%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERipples%20of%20change%3A%20Turning%20ideas%20into%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20began%20the%20entangling%20and%20detangling%20of%20more%20threads.%20The%20students%20had%20the%20arduous%20task%20of%20connecting%20the%20dots%20between%20the%20water%20crisis%20and%20the%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshita%2C%20a%20student%2C%20observed%20a%20distinct%20connection%20between%20their%20school%20coursework%20and%20the%20questions%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20find%20answers%20to.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20special%20science%2C%20we%20learned%20about%20the%20types%20of%20rain.%20Our%20science%20curriculum%20helped%20us%20understand%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20layout%20and%20the%20materials%20it%20was%20built%20with.%20For%20measuring%20rain%2C%20we%20turned%20to%20maths.%20And%20to%20understand%20people%E2%80%99s%20perspectives%2C