.com%2F%3Fp%3D386842%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Beyond%20the%20snow%2C%20these%20hidden%20winter%20festivals%20shine%2C%20bringing%20together%20culture%2C%20faith%2C%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20regions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386842%2Fwinter-festivals-india-tibetan-new-year-losar-magh-mela-himachal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chef%E2%80%99s%20Choice%3A%207%20Must-Visit%20Spots%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20Best%20Samosas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20fast-changing%20landscape%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy%20has%20seen%20many%20recipes%20come%20and%20go.%20Some%20are%20fleeting%2C%20but%20then%20there%20are%20also%20the%20constants%2C%20embedded%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20social%20fabric.%20One%20such%20time-tested%20snack%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(savoury%20Indian%20pastry).%20Known%20for%20its%20penchant%20for%20breathing%20life%20into%20dull%20evenings%20and%20sleepy%20mornings%2C%20the%20culinary%20wonder%20reigns%20over%20the%20food%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20asked%20chefs%2C%20bloggers%2C%20and%20those%20familiar%20with%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy%20where%20they%20head%20for%20their%20fill%20of%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Mandi%20House%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20epicentre%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20culture%20and%20art%20worlds%2C%20Mandi%20House%20has%20often%20been%20described%20as%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20own%20%E2%80%98Broadway%E2%80%99.%20The%20story%20behind%20the%20name%20traces%20back%20to%20when%20the%20area%20belonged%20to%20the%20Raja%20of%20Mandi.%20Its%20long%20legacy%20has%20witnessed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F257070%2Fkerala-puppet-dying-art-heritage-nokkuvidya-pavakkali-padma-shri-moozhik