024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-150x267.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388047%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPutul%20is%20a%20home-grown%20film%20with%20no%20foreign%20collaboration%2C%20and%20receiving%20a%20standing%20ovation%20during%20its%20screening%20in%20a%20mid-sized%20theatre%20was%20purely%20magical.%20Hearing%20praise%20from%20esteemed%20filmmakers%20like%20Aniruddha%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20and%20Margaret%20Zambonini%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Ardenslate%20(a%20script%20development%20company)%2C%20was%20an%20unforgettable%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20occasion%2C%20Indira%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20mainstream%20films%20with%20big%20stars%20were%20struggling%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20seven%20Indian%20films%20screened%20at%20Cannes%20brought%20pride%20and%20joy%20to%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20films%20that%20represented%20India%20%E2%80%94%20Indira%20herself%20carried%20her%20culture%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CIndira%20being%20Indira%2C%20honoured%20her%20roots%20and%20culture%20even%20on%20an%20international%20stage%20like%20Cannes.%20She%20began%20her%20speech%20in%20Bangla%20before%20switching%20to%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayan%20fondly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%E2%80%99s%20poster%20and%20teaser%20were%20also%20launched%20at%20Cannes%2C%20and%20Sayan%20recounts%20the%20surreal%20moment%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F133350%2Fbhanu-athaiya-unsung-woman-won-indias-1st-oscar-long-ar-rahman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20R%20Rahman%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoted%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20someone%20from%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20having%20Rahman%20acknowledge%20a%20film%20you%20have%20worked%20on%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20has%20earned%20international%20acclaim%20%E2%80%94%20is%20surreal%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayan%20stood%20as%20a%20pillar%20of%20constant%20support%20throughout%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20to%20name%20one%20person%20who%20stood%20by%20me%20and%20my%20work%2C%20it%20would%20be%20Sayan%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Indira.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20director%2C%20who%20is%20always%20acknowledging%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20needs%20appreciation%20too.%20Sayan%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20achieve%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%2C%20Indira%20is%20already%20working%20on%20a%20new%20Hindi%20project%2C%20a%20biopic%20featuring%20Divya%20Dutta%20and%20Neeraj%20Kabi%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20works%20of%20legendary%20filmmaker%20Shyam%20Benegal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20to%20be%20screened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20aspiring%20filmmakers%2C%20Indira%20has%20some%20simple%20yet%20powerful%20advice%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20background%20hold%20you%20back.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a