e%20petals%20in%20his%20solar%20dryer.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishadh-with-rose-flowers-on-dryer_11zon-1733937645.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishadh-with-rose-flowers-on-dryer_11zon-1733937645-300x219.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishadh-with-rose-flowers-on-dryer_11zon-1733937645-500x365.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishadh-with-rose-flowers-on-dryer_11zon-1733937645-768x560.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishadh-with-rose-flowers-on-dryer_11zon-1733937645-150x109.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388815%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENishad%20checking%20on%20the%20dehydrated%20rose%20petals%20in%20his%20solar%20dryer.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20stands%20first%20in%20dry%20flower%20exports%20due%20to%20its%20wide%20availability%20of%20various%20plant%20species.%20Dried%20flowers%20are%20exported%20to%20the%20USA%2C%20Japan%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20The%20export%20industry%20for%20dried%20flowers%20and%20plants%20from%20India%20is%20valued%20at%20around%20Rs%20100%20crore%20annually%2C%20with%20over%20500%20varieties%20being%20shipped%20to%2020%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNishad%E2%80%99s%20success%20has%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20numerous%20farmers%20from%20his%20region%2C%20leading%20over%20100%20farmers%20to%20collaborate%20by%20supplying%20raw%20materials%2C%20thereby%20improving%20their%20livelihoods.%20His%20story%20inspires%20other%20farmers%20to%20leverage%20the%20locally%20available%20farm%20produce%2C%20cater%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20food%20loss%2Fspoilage%2C%20and%20integrate%20innovative%20clean-energy-powered%20livelihood%20tech