ation-sharvan-patel-rajasthan-whatsapp-group-save-species-habitats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20controlled%20hunting%2C%20and%20over%20the%20years%2C%20it%20evolved%20into%20the%20wildlife%20sanctuary%20it%20is%20today.%20In%201999%2C%20it%20officially%20became%20Orang%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%94%20a%20protected%20area%20with%20a%20rich%20history%20and%20even%20richer%20biodiversity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20park%20is%20located%20in%20an%20alluvial%20floodplain%2C%20formed%20by%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20several%20rivers%2C%20including%20the%20Pachnoi%2C%20Belsiri%2C%20and%20Dhansiri%2C%20which%20join%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20This%20geography%20makes%20the%20park%20especially%20vulnerable%20to%20seasonal%20flooding%2C%20but%20also%20supports%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20plant%20and%20animal%20life%2C%20including%2012%20natural%20wetlands%20and%2026%20artificial%20water%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20wildlife%20of%20Orang%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Orang%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20strengths%20is%20its%20impressive%20array%20of%20wildlife.%20The%20park%20is%20most%20famous%20for%20being%20the%20northernmost%20stronghold%20of%20the%20great%20Indian%20one-horned%20rhinoceros.%20As%20per%202022%20numbers%2C%20it%20is%20home%20to%20around%20125%20rhinos%2C%20the%20numbers%20for%20which%20have%20been%20steadily%20increasing.%20The%20park%20also%20houses%20a%20variety%20of%20other%20large%20mammals%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Asiatic%20elephant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wild%20water%20buffalo%2C%20and%20the%20hog%20deer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20750